title: Reward those who provide liquidity through migration
body:
SBF is giving out 1mm $SUSHI for those who continue to provide liquidity through migration. (https://twitter.com/SBF_Alameda/status/1302967576968880130?s=20)

This proposal is to match the amount given out by SBF and provide another 1mm $SUSHI from treasury to those who continue to stake liquidity through migration.
